## Getting Started

### 1. Environment Setup
```bash
# Clone and navigate to project
cd edgar

# Create virtual environment
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Test API Access
```bash
# Test basic EDGAR API functionality
python3 test_edgar_api.py
```

### 3. Run Prototype
```bash
# Run the prototype analyzer
python3 edgar_analyzer_prototype.py
```

